<br>
The small candle had been consumed long ago, but the pale light from the stars entered through the window, and that was more than enough for reading... if you have elven eyes. He took some notes and smiled to himself, as he found an obscure reference about how to defeat a nasty creature. Worth to check if it's true, he thought.<br>
<br>
Suddenly it all came again. The pain, the violent coughing, the blood. He fell unconscious, books and scrolls all around him on the floor. The last thing he remembered was the words of that old man in Felwithe. <br>
<br>
&quot;You are cursed, there is no cure, In three moons you shall die&quot; <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.hi-logic.com/chosenspirit/Echtelion_sig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
