<br>
Gripping his cramping stomach and shoving another half-melted snowball down his pants, Neomiah looks around to see the crowd to include Binka and Farbria laughing hysterically at him...<br>
<br>
&quot;What!?  You think it's funny to unintentionally soil yourself in public or to put Halas' Icy Hot in the ointment for ones backside!!!&quot; yells Neomiah<br>
<br>
Binka and Farbria go quiet realizing the joke has cut deeper into Neomiahs soul than any blade could do.<br>
<br>
&quot;I didnt think some innocent flirtation would result in this....I know when I am not wanted...&quot;<br>
<br>
Neomiah winces in pain as he bends over to pick up his scattered gear.<br>
<br>
The Ogre whom Neomiah had knocked the beer onto spots the perfect time for a bit of revenge...<br>
<br>
&quot;Yo dorf, you owez me anutter beer... &quot;  the Ogre winds up and lets loose a mighty kick to Neomiah's injured backside, which launching the little Dwarf 10 feet across the room and landing at Binka's feet.  <br>
<br>
Neomiah looks up into the eyes of the crimson haired barbarian, his tears of physical pain have clearly turned to tears of anguish.<br>
<br>
&quot;Neo I'm...&quot;<br>
<br>
Neomiah turns away and scurries out the door of the bar sobbing... <br>
<br>
